a:5:{s:5:"title";s:54:"OpenCRM extends Email Plans to support SMS scheduling";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:606:"<p>OpenCRM updated its Email Plans feature so it can now schedule SMS/text messages in addition to email.</p>
<p>What changed</p>
<p>Email Plans can now schedule one SMS or a series of SMS messages.</p>
<p>SMS can be sent to Leads and Contacts.</p>
<p>Why it matters</p>
<p>Teams using Email Plans for timed outreach can now manage email + SMS follow-ups through the same scheduling workflow, reducing manual reminders and keeping contact sequences consistent.</p>
<p>Learn more: <a href="https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/392">https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/392</a></p>
";s:9:"text-flow";a:7:{i:0;s:102:"OpenCRM updated its Email Plans feature so it can now schedule SMS/text messages in addition to email.";i:1;s:12:"What changed";i:2;s:65:"Email Plans can now schedule one SMS or a series of SMS messages.";i:3;s:38:"SMS can be sent to Leads and Contacts.";i:4;s:14:"Why it matters";i:5;s:186:"Teams using Email Plans for timed outreach can now manage email + SMS follow-ups through the same scheduling workflow, reducing manual reminders and keeping contact sequences consistent.";i:6;s:60:"Learn more: https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/392";}s:4:"meta";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}}s:7:"summary";s:137:"OpenCRM updated its Email Plans feature so it can now schedule SMS/text messages in addition to email. | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:9:"tags-data";a:2:{s:5:"ctree";a:3:{i:0;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:34:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";}i:1;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:7:"opencrm";s:4:"href";s:38:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/opencrm/";}i:2;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:46:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";}}s:20:"all-resnames-uploads";a:0:{}}}